            We use a pay-per-lead model with no upfront costs or monthly fees. You only pay when we send you a qualified lead that matches your service area and specialties. Payment terms and lead pricing are discussed during the application process based on your location and services offered.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ Item 2 -->
        <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 flex items-center gap-3">
            <i data-lucide="shield-check" class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600"></i>
            What licenses and insurance do I need?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            You must have a valid Michigan HVAC contractor license and current general liability insurance. We also require proof of workers' compensation insurance if you have employees. All licenses and insurance must remain current throughout your participation in our network.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ Item 3 -->
        <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 flex items-center gap-3">
            <i data-lucide="map-pin" class="w-6 h-6 text-red-600"></i>
            Can I choose which areas I serve?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Absolutely. During application, you specify your service areas down to specific cities or zip codes. We only send leads within your designated service territory. You can update your service areas at any time as your business grows or changes.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ Item 4 -->
        <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 flex items-center gap-3">
            <i data-lucide="settings" class="w-6 h-6 text-orange-600"></i>
            How do I control the number of leads I receive?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            You set your own capacity limits when you join. You can specify how many leads you want per week, pause lead delivery when you're fully booked, or increase volume during slower periods. We provide an easy dashboard to manage your availability and lead preferences.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ Item 5 -->
        <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 flex items-center gap-3">
            <i data-lucide="clock" class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600"></i>
            How quickly will I start receiving leads?
          </h3>
