            Once approved and onboarded, most contractors receive their first leads within 1-2 weeks. Lead volume depends on your service area, season, and local demand. Emergency service providers typically see leads faster than installation-only contractors.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ Item 6 -->
        <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 flex items-center gap-3">
            <i data-lucide="users" class="w-6 h-6 text-indigo-600"></i>
            Do you share leads with multiple contractors?
          </h3>
