          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ Item 7 -->
        <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 flex items-center gap-3">
            <i data-lucide="star" class="w-6 h-6 text-yellow-600"></i>
            What's expected of me as a network provider?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            We expect professional, timely service with fair pricing. You should respond to leads quickly (within 2-4 hours), provide accurate quotes, and deliver quality work. We track customer satisfaction and may remove providers who consistently receive poor feedback.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ Item 8 -->
        <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 flex items-center gap-3">
            <i data-lucide="x-circle" class="w-6 h-6 text-red-600"></i>
            Can I leave the network at any time?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Yes, there are no long-term contracts or cancellation fees. You can pause or permanently leave the network at any time with 30 days' notice. You'll remain responsible for any outstanding lead fees, but there are no penalties for leaving.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ Item 9 -->
        <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 flex items-center gap-3">
            <i data-lucide="phone" class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600"></i>
