            We provide dedicated contractor support via phone and email. Our team understands the HVAC business and can help with lead quality issues, billing questions, or technical problems. Most issues are resolved within 24 hours.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ Item 10 -->
        <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 flex items-center gap-3">
            <i data-lucide="trending-up" class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600"></i>
