          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Furnace repairs, especially during fall/winter months, generate the highest volume. Emergency no-heat calls are frequent and urgent. Installation leads are less frequent but higher value. Maintenance and duct cleaning provide steady year-round opportunities.
          </p>
        </div>
